  "body_html": "<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content\" typography=\"classic\"><p id=\"ucf18f904\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">折叠块是一种布局卡片，当文档的篇幅过长时，折叠块可以灵活展开收起，让内容有详有略地呈现。</span></p><div data-type=\"tips\" class=\"ne-alert\"><p id=\"u29542bf4\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1655119363012-f5cd8fd8-2bc7-411f-ae96-ca2a716f859b.png\" width=\"283\" id=\"u0bb0d2a8\" class=\"ne-image\"></p></div><h2 id=\"Uosdm\"><span class=\"ne-text\">添加折叠块</span></h2><h3 id=\"uNkC7\"><span class=\"ne-text\">1. 点击添加</span></h3><p id=\"u46cac872\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">点击左上角的插入面板，选择折叠块。</span></p><p id=\"ue2304e3c\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1655099350094-1981faba-bee9-4d8b-a571-35ca762d2224.png\" width=\"308\" id=\"MivMt\" class=\"ne-image\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1655114759322-904fde79-923e-42a9-b050-5349a337895c.png\" width=\"283\" id=\"u7cc504f2\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><h3 id=\"pqxLF\"><span class=\"ne-text\">2. 斜杠输入</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">/zdk</span></code></h3><p id=\"u475ca9af\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">在正文区域输入 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">/zdk</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">、</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">/折叠</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，选择折叠块。</span></p><p id=\"u920f9859\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-indent: 2em\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1655100645430-54fd1170-a212-4b77-a8bd-f09ffaed8db1.png\" width=\"311\" id=\"u78947c7d\" class=\"ne-image\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1655114778217-9438edd0-aefb-4fac-ae7a-fe70d03a21c1.png\" width=\"282\" id=\"ue74cb52b\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"u4b36ce32\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h2 id=\"OaB73\"><span class=\"ne-text\">设置格式</span></h2><p id=\"uc2341b26\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">折叠块由两部分组成：折叠块标题和折叠区内容。</span></p><p id=\"ub06caded\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">建议输入折叠块标题，这样在阅读端的层级展现更清晰。</span></p><p id=\"u93b730dd\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1655126455730-06ed324e-1d10-4be7-9f0a-c12b66c8a77e.png\" width=\"754\" id=\"uf105652e\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><h3 id=\"H2WBB\"><span class=\"ne-text\">设置标题</span></h3><p id=\"u1474c181\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">可以对折叠块标题进行有限的样式设置。</span></p><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u569d3a89\"><span class=\"ne-text\">如 </span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">加粗</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">、</span><em><span class=\"ne-text\">斜体</span></em><span class=\"ne-text\">、</span><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"text-decoration: line-through\">删除线</span><span class=\"ne-text\">、</span><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"text-decoration: underline\">下划线</span><span class=\"ne-text\">、</span><sup><span class=\"ne-text\">上标</span></sup><span class=\"ne-text\">、</span><sub><span class=\"ne-text\">下标</span></sub><span class=\"ne-text\">、</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">行内代码</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">、</span><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #2F54EB\">字体颜色</span><span class=\"ne-text\">和</span><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"background-color: #B7EB8F\">背景颜色</span><span class=\"ne-text\">等。</span></li></ul><p id=\"u9fc5cf09\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1655126881381-397b469f-e93a-4717-82f3-0d676e2de192.png\" width=\"291\" id=\"ue6f870ac\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><h3 id=\"sssll\"><span class=\"ne-text\">设置内容</span></h3><p id=\"ubd0406c2\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">折叠块内支持嵌入多种内容。包括富文本段落、引用、分割线、高亮块、图片、附件、链接、标题、卡片等。</span></p><details class=\"lake-collapse\"><summary id=\"u5cde1f4e\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgb(38, 38, 38)\">像书一样的知识库</span></summary><div class=\"ne-quote\"><p id=\"u7318306a\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgb(88, 90, 90)\">语雀特色的目录及大纲功能，让多篇文档结构化，形成一本本像书一样清晰易读的知识库，方便知识 创作及沉淀。</span></p></div><div data-type=\"tips\" class=\"ne-alert\"><h4 id=\"HXP7V\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgb(38, 38, 38)\">目录编排\t</span><a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/yuque/thyzgp/vlki63\" data-href=\"https://www.yuque.com/yuque/thyzgp/vlki63\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"ne-link\"><span class=\"ne-text\">了解更多</span></a></h4><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u650d32c6\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgb(88, 90, 90); background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250)\">简单、强大的目录编辑，让你的知识库文档结构可以和书本一样清晰易读</span></li></ul></div><div data-type=\"tips\" class=\"ne-alert\"><h4 id=\"ye0JA\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgb(38, 38, 38); background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250); font-size: 19px\">互动交流</span></h4><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u351a6e39\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgb(88, 90, 90); background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250)\">创作之外，让所有成员可以在同一个地方进行互动交流，让想法碰撞更有趣，沟通更充分。</span></li></ul></div><div data-type=\"tips\" class=\"ne-alert\"><h4 id=\"FVUoL\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgb(38, 38, 38); background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250); font-size: 19px\">权限管理\t</span><a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/yuque/qa/kybteg\" data-href=\"https://www.yuque.com/yuque/qa/kybteg\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"ne-link\"><span class=\"ne-text\">了解更多</span></a></h4><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u6aa725ce\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgb(88, 90, 90); background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250)\">可以对知识库人员进行精细化管理，按需调整只读、编辑复制、分享，下载等相关权限，安全尽在掌握</span></li></ul></div><p id=\"u3693fbe0\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1655128326157-c97f0dd0-068e-4cd9-a0c5-18e576063148.png\" width=\"427\" id=\"u8281a2a3\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><div id=\"o233y\" class=\"ne-yuque\">此处为语雀内容卡片，点击链接查看：<a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/yuque/changelog/roadmap#sAFb4AQIyGg9hMH2pYnM6fX71dnqIkXo\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.yuque.com/yuque/changelog/roadmap#sAFb4AQIyGg9hMH2pYnM6fX71dnqIkXo</a></div></details><h2 id=\"ijXct\"><span class=\"ne-text\">阅读端展示</span></h2><p id=\"uc0fcfc61\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">在编辑端会显示折叠块的轮廓描边，在阅读端会隐藏折叠块的边框。</span></p><p id=\"uc424fa92\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1655128869862-3556d5c9-e931-4aa6-832d-889bbe5061d5.png\" width=\"750\" id=\"uc535d067\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"uda53fa18\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1655128963962-427321f5-8eed-453e-b036-8a6b54a11dca.png\" width=\"832\" id=\"u77bbc11b\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><h2 id=\"Oa0cl\"><span class=\"ne-text\">折叠状态继承</span></h2><p id=\"uc01de200\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">编辑端点击发布后，编辑端设置的折叠块收起/展开的样式，会成为阅读端默认的样式。<br /></span><span class=\"ne-text\">阅读者可以点击展开收起。</span></p></div>",
  "slug": 80286693,
  "title": "如何插入折叠块"
}